      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALFNALMA (9) hasn't featured in her last two outings in the city but will relish the return to a venue where she has won six of nine attempts, coming from a wide barrier to score in her last visit three back. Can settle just behind them and wait on the sprint lane so could add to her impressive strike rate here. THE SWIFT ONE (5) turned in another strong performance last time when she battled on bravely to just miss out by a nose, adding to a series of top-three results at this venue that includes a win from a similar draw two back. Big chance. BORROWED TIME (6) was fair in finishing fifth from this barrier last week but has definite claims off a win here three back. MAC THUNDER (1) has won at this circuit and distance before and hasn't been too far off the placings in both outings since he came from this barrier for a close second at Penrith.",
